    "description": "The <strong>Evolution of War</strong> game shows the evolution of warfare in 5 ages, starting with the age of dinosaurs, crusades, medieval, 21st century (present time) and futuristic (fiction).<br>The game's main objective is to destroy the enemy base, but for that to happen you'll need to defend yourself and attack by planning a good strategy.<br>You can select up to 3 types of soldiers to put into battle being one of the weakest, medium and strongest in each era, however you will need to have the necessary money to buy them.<br>You can add new weapons to the base, which can include up to 6 weapons, each additional weapon has a cost. Where you earn money by killing enemy troops and attacking the enemy base.",
